headline: Does C.H. Robinson’s (CHRW) New Asset Management System Mark a Turning Point in Digital Logistics?
summary: C.H. Robinson Worldwide showcased its technology advancements at the CSCMP EDGE 2025 Conference on October 6, highlighting the launch of its Asset Management System (AMS) that provides real-time trailer visibility and operational data. A unique takeaway is the company's focus on unlocking operational efficiency and proactive exception management for shippers, underscoring broader efforts to enhance the value of logistics through digitalization.
